data.description: Four-sided brick home nestled in the prestigious, sought-after Southland Country Club neighborhood. Traditional grace & style but with a modern updated open floor plan! Best of both worlds!  Situated on a tranquil street, this home features 4 large bedrooms, 2 ½ Bathrooms, Hardwood Laminate floors, Solid Surface Countertops, and a Kitchen with sight lines to the Family Room.  Walk into your new Executive home through the open foyer and quickly notice the craftsmanship details that are present throughout this home.  The Oversized Owner’s Suite features tray ceilings and a separate seating area or potential attached nursery room! New Roof in 2017.  Exterior updates include hardscape retaining walls, brick tree surrounds, and underground downspout drainage.   The spa-like Owner’s bath features dual vanities, a tub, and a separate shower! The home receives ample amounts of natural light! This Highly Desired Golf Community features Resort-Style amenities, complete with Tennis Courts, Pool, golf & a play area for the kids.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning home your own!
